{"kanda":6,"sarga":85,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"त्तस्यतद्वचनंश्रुत्वाराघवश्शोककर्शितः ।नोपधारयतेव्यक्तंयदुक्तंतेनरक्षसा","trans":"Immersed in grief, Raghava could not make out the words spoken by Vibheeshana.","words":[{"d":"शोककर्शितः","m":"immersed in grief"},{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"तत्","m":"those"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"having heard"},{"d":"तेन","m":"by that रक्षसा Rakshasa"},{"d":"यत्","m":"which"},{"d":"उक्तम्","m":"was"},{"d":"व्यक्तम्","m":"spoken"},{"d":"नोपधारयते","m":"could not know"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"ततोधैर्यमवष्टभ्यरामःपरपुरञ्जयः ।विभीषणमुपासीनमुवाचकपिसन्निधौ","trans":"Then Rama, who can win over enemies, picked up courage, said to Vibheeshana seated near him in front of Vanaras.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"परपुरञ्जयः","m":"who can win over enemies"},{"d":"रामः","m":"Rama"},{"d":"धैर्यम्","m":"courage"},{"d":"अवष्टभ्य","m":"picked up"},{"d":"उपासीनम्","m":"seated near"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"कपिसन्निधौ","m":"in front of Vanaras"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"said"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"नैरृताधिपतेवाक्यंयदुक्तंतेविभीषण ।भूयस्तच्छ्रोतुमिच्छामिब्रूहियत्तेविवक्षितम्","trans":"\"O Lord of Rakshasas, Vibheeshana! I wish to hear the words spoken by you. You may repeat that which you wanted to convey. I wish to hear.\"","words":[{"d":"नैरृताधिपते","m":"Rakshasa (progeny of Nirriti presiding the southwest)"},{"d":"विभीषण","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that which"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"उक्तम्","m":"spoken"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"श्रोतुम्","m":"wish to hear"},{"d":"इच्छामि","m":"wish"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that which"},{"d":"इवक्षितम्","m":"to be conveyed"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"भूयः","m":"repeat again"},{"d":"श्रोतुम्","m":"wish to hear"},{"d":"इच्छामि","m":"desire"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"राघवस्यवचःश्रुत्वावाक्यंवाक्यविशारद. ।यत्तत्पुनरिदंवाक्यंबभाषे स विभीषणः","trans":"Vibheeshana, who was skilled in expression, spoke again as follows on hearing Raghava's words.","words":[{"d":"सःविभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"उदाहृतम्","m":"skilled in expression"},{"d":"राघवस्य","m":"Raghava's"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"इदंवाक्यम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"यत्नात्","m":"to him"},{"d":"बभाषे","m":"spoke again"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"यथाज्ञप्तंमहाबाहोत्वयागुल्मनिवेशनम् ।तत्तथाऽनुष्ठितंवीरत्वद्वाक्यसमनन्तरम्","trans":"\" After your command the army has been divided and placed at respective places as you said.\"","words":[{"d":"महाबाहो","m":"mighty armed"},{"d":"वीर","m":"hero"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"गुल्मनिवेशनम्","m":"from their respective places"},{"d":"यथा","m":"that which"},{"d":"आज्ञप्तम्","m":"command"},{"d":"तत्","m":"then"},{"d":"त्वदाक्यसमनन्तरम्","m":"according to your order"},{"d":"तथा","m":"like that"},{"d":"अनुष्ठितम्","m":"has been done"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"तान्यनीकानिसर्वाणिविभग्नानिसमन्ततः ।विन्यस्तायूथपाश्चैवयथान्यायंविभागशः","trans":"All the army forces have been collected, divided, and assigned to respective places separately.","words":[{"d":"तानि","m":"all of them"},{"d":"अनीकानि","m":"army forces"},{"d":"सर्वाणि","m":"all"},{"d":"विभक्तानि","m":"divided"},{"d":"यूथपाश्चैव","m":"where ever"},{"d":"यथान्यायम्","m":"in the respective places"},{"d":"विभागशः","m":"separately"},{"d":"विन्यस्ताः","m":"assigned"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"भूयस्तुममविज्ञाप्यंतच्छ्रुणुष्वमहायश: ।त्वय्यकारणसन्तप्तेसन्तप्तहृदयावयम्","trans":"\"O great Lord! Hear me, which is yet to be submitted by me to you. You are afflicted without cause and pained at heart.\"","words":[{"d":"महाप्रभो","m":"O great Lord"},{"d":"भूयः","m":"being"},{"d":"मम","m":"me"},{"d":"विज्ञाप्यम्","m":"which is to be submitted"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"शृणुष्व","m":"hear"},{"d":"त्वयि","m":"to you"},{"d":"अकारणसन्तप्ते","m":"afflicted without any cause"},{"d":"वयम्","m":"you"},{"d":"सन्तप्तहृदयाः","m":"pained at heart"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"त्यजराजन्निमंशोकंमिथ्यासन्तापमागतम् ।तदियंत्यज्यतांचिन्ताशत्रुहर्षविवर्धिनी","trans":"\"O king! Give up this false agony which has set in. It enhances the joy of the enemy. Give up this anxiety.\"","words":[{"d":"राजन्","m":"king"},{"d":"इमम्","m":"this"},{"d":"शोकम्","m":"agony"},{"d":"मिथ्या","m":"false"},{"d":"आगतम्","m":"has set in"},{"d":"सन्तापम्","m":"worry"},{"d":"त्यज","m":"give up"},{"d":"तत्","m":"then"},{"d":"शत्रुहर्षविवर्धिनी","m":"it enhances the joy of enemy"},{"d":"इयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"चिन्ता","m":"anxiety"},{"d":"त्यज्यताम्","m":"giveup"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"उद्यमःक्रियतांवीरहर्षःसमुपसेव्यताम् ।प्राप्तव्यायदितेसीताहन्तव्याश्चनिशाचराः","trans":"\"Let efforts be made to recover Sita. Let enthusiasm be restored to recover Sita. Rakshasas will be exterminated.\"","words":[{"d":"वीर","m":"hero"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"सीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"प्राप्तव्या","m":"attain"},{"d":"निशाचराः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"हन्तव्याश्च","m":"will be exterminated"},{"d":"उद्यमः","m":"effort"},{"d":"क्रियताम्","m":"resorted"},{"d":"हर्षः","m":"enthusiasm"},{"d":"समुपसेव्यताम्","m":"will recover"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"रघुनन्दनवक्ष्यामिश्रूयतांमेहितंवचः ।साध्वयंयातुसौमित्रिर्बलेनमहतावृतः निकुम्भिलायांसम्प्राप्यहन्तुंरावणिमाहवे ।धनुर्मण्डलनिर्मुक्तैराशीविषविषोपमैः","trans":"\"Delight of Raghus! You may listen to my words of advice. Let Saumithri march ahead to Nikumbhilam accompanied by the great army. On reaching, let Lakshmana who is capable of killing Indrajith discharge venomous serpents like deadly poisonous arrows from his bow in circular form and kill Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"रघुनन्दन","m":"delight of Raghus"},{"d":"मे","m":"my"},{"d":"हितम्","m":"advice"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रूयताम्","m":"you may listen"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"सौमित्रिः","m":"Saumithri"},{"d":"महता","m":"great"},{"d":"बलेन","m":"army"},{"d":"वृतः","m":"surrounded"},{"d":"निकुम्भिलायाम्","m":"Nikumbhilam"},{"d":"सम्प्राप्तम्","m":"reach"},{"d":"रावणिम्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"आहवे","m":"on reaching"},{"d":"धनुर्मण्डलनिर्मुक्तै:","m":"discharged from his bow in circular form"},{"d":"आशीविषविषोपमैः","m":"like deadly poison of venomous serpents"},{"d":"हन्तुम्","m":"kill"},{"d":"साधु","m":"excellent"},{"d":"यातु","m":"march ahead"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"रघुनन्दनवक्ष्यामिश्रूयतांमेहितंवचः ।साध्वयंयातुसौमित्रिर्बलेनमहतावृतः निकुम्भिलायांसम्प्राप्यहन्तुंरावणिमाहवे ।धनुर्मण्डलनिर्मुक्तैराशीविषविषोपमैः","trans":"\"Delight of Raghus! You may listen to my words of advice. Let Saumithri march ahead to Nikumbhilam accompanied by the great army. On reaching, let Lakshmana who is capable of killing Indrajith discharge venomous serpents like deadly poisonous arrows from his bow in circular form and kill Rakshasas.\"","words":[{"d":"रघुनन्दन","m":"delight of Raghus"},{"d":"मे","m":"my"},{"d":"हितम्","m":"advice"},{"d":"वचः","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रूयताम्","m":"you may listen"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"सौमित्रिः","m":"Saumithri"},{"d":"महता","m":"great"},{"d":"बलेन","m":"army"},{"d":"वृतः","m":"surrounded"},{"d":"निकुम्भिलायाम्","m":"Nikumbhilam"},{"d":"सम्प्राप्तम्","m":"reach"},{"d":"रावणिम्","m":"Indrajith"},{"d":"आहवे","m":"on reaching"},{"d":"धनुर्मण्डलनिर्मुक्तै:","m":"discharged from his bow in circular form"},{"d":"आशीविषविषोपमैः","m":"like deadly poison of venomous serpents"},{"d":"हन्तुम्","m":"kill"},{"d":"साधु","m":"excellent"},{"d":"यातु","m":"march ahead"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"तेनवीरेणतपसावरदानात्स्वयम्भुवः ।अस्त्रंब्रह्मशिरःप्राप्तंकामगाश्चतुरङ्गमाः","trans":"\"Lakshmana, being heroic received Brahmasira weapon from the creator by austerity and also horses which can course according to his will.\"","words":[{"d":"वीरेण","m":"being hero"},{"d":"तेन","m":"by him"},{"d":"तपसा","m":"by austerity"},{"d":"स्वयम्भुवः","m":"creator"},{"d":"वरदानात्","m":"boon received"},{"d":"ब्रह्मशिरः","m":"Brahmasira weapon"},{"d":"अस्त्रम्","m":"arrow"},{"d":"प्राप्तम्","m":"attained"},{"d":"कामगाः","m":"coursing at his will"},{"d":"तुरङ्गमाः","m":"horses"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"स एषसहसैन्येनप्राप्तःकिलनिकुम्भिलाम् ।यद्युततिष्ठेत्कृतंकर्महतान्सर्वांश्चविद्धिनः","trans":"\"Indrajith has reached Nikumbhilam accompanied by the army. If he completes the sacrifice and comes from there after completion of the sacrifice, know that we are all killed.","words":[{"d":"सःएषः","m":"he in that way"},{"d":"सैन्येनसह","m":"accompanied by army"},{"d":"निकुम्भिलाम्","m":"Nikumbhilam"},{"d":"प्राप्तःकिल","m":"reached"},{"d":"कर्म","m":"act of sacrifice"},{"d":"कृतम्","m":"doing"},{"d":"उततिष्ठेद्यदि","m":"comes from there"},{"d":"सर्वान्","m":"all"},{"d":"हतान्","m":"killed"},{"d":"विद्धि","m":"know"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"निकुम्भिलामसम्प्राप्तमहुताग्निं च योरिपुः ।त्वामातायिनंहन्यादिन्द्रशत्रोस्सतेवधः वरोदत्तोमहाबाहो सर्वलोकेश्वरेणवै ।इत्येवंविहितोराजन्वधस्तस्यैषधीमतः","trans":"\"O mighty armed Rama! that enemy of yours, while you have not reached Nikumbhilam and not propitiated fire sacrifice, can cause your death. Such a boon was granted to him, the enemy of Indra by the Lord of all worlds.\"","words":[{"d":"महाबाहो","m":"mightyarmed"},{"d":"इन्द्रशत्रो","m":"enemy of Indra"},{"d":"यः","m":"he who"},{"d":"रिपुः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"निकुम्भिलाम्","m":"Nikumbhilam"},{"d":"असम्प्राप्तम्","m":"not reached"},{"d":"आहुताग्निं च","m":"propitiated your fire"},{"d":"आततायिनम्","m":"cause of your death"},{"d":"त्वाम्","m":"you"},{"d":"हन्यात्","m":"killed"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"वधः","m":"kill"},{"d":"सर्वलोकेश्वरेण","m":"Lord of all worlds"},{"d":"धीमतः","m":"wise"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"इत्येवम्","m":"in this way"},{"d":"वरः","m":"boon"},{"d":"एषः","m":"that way"},{"d":"विहितः","m":"ordained"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"निकुम्भिलामसम्प्राप्तमहुताग्निं च योरिपुः ।त्वामातायिनंहन्यादिन्द्रशत्रोस्सतेवधः वरोदत्तोमहाबाहो सर्वलोकेश्वरेणवै ।इत्येवंविहितोराजन्वधस्तस्यैषधीमतः","trans":"\"O mighty armed Rama! that enemy of yours, while you have not reached Nikumbhilam and not propitiated fire sacrifice, can cause your death. Such a boon was granted to hi