se of Brahma's weapon, intelligent in conjuring, endowed with mighty prowess, and can make even varuna and Devatas unconscious.","words":[{"d":"ब्रह्मास्त्रवित्","m":"skilled in the use of Brahma's weapon"},{"d":"प्राज्ञः","m":"wise"},{"d":"महामायः","m":"intelligent in conjuring"},{"d":"सवरुणान्","m":"Varuna and others"},{"d":"देवानपि","m":"Devatas also"},{"d":"सङ्ग्रामे","m":"in war"},{"d":"असंज्ञान्","m":"unconscious"},{"d":"करोति","m":"does"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"तस्यान्तरिक्षेचरतःसरथस्यमहायशः ।न गतिर्ज्ञायतेवीरसूर्यस्येवाभ्रसम्ल्पवे","trans":"When he moves in his chariot in the sky like the Sun coursing through clouds is difficult to know.","words":[{"d":"महायशः","m":"of great fame"},{"d":"वीर","m":"hero"},{"d":"सरथस्य","m":"with that chariot"},{"d":"अन्तरिक्षे","m":"sky"},{"d":"चरतः","m":"going"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"गतिः","m":"movement"},{"d":"अभ्रसम्प्लवे","m":"coursing through clouds"}]},{"v":20,"dev":"राघवस्तुरिपोर्ज्ञात्वामायावीर्यंदुरात्मनः ।लक्ष्मणंकीर्तिसम्पन्नमिदंवचनमब्रवीत्","trans":"Knowing the wickedminded enemy of conjuring valour, Rama spoke as follows to Lakshmana, richly endowed with fame (of winning wars).","words":[{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"दुरात्मनः","m":"wicked minded"},{"d":"रिपोः","m":"enemy"},{"d":"मायावीर्यम्","m":"conjuring valour"},{"d":"ज्ञात्वा","m":"knowing"},{"d":"कीर्तिसम्पन्नम्","m":"richly endowed with fame"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"इदंवचनम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":21,"dev":"यद्वानरेन्द्रस्यबलंतेनसर्वेणसम्वृतः ।हनूमत्प्रमुखैश्चवयूथपैस्सहलक्ष्मण जाम्बवेनार्क्षपतिनासहसैन्येनसम्वृतः ।जहितंराक्षससुतंमायाबलविशारदम्","trans":"\"O Lakshmana! Surrounded by the entire army of Vanara king, with Hanuman as commander in chief of the army, protected by Jambavan, king of Bears, put an end to the son of Ravana who is well versed in tricks.\"","words":[{"d":"लक्ष्मण","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"वानरेन्द्रस्य","m":"Vanara king's"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that which"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"army"},{"d":"ते